  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Fallow City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/fdbfde4fd9a01bd1c5a448e964520007.avif?t=1772189407\" width=600 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Fallow City is an Indie Horror, Action-Adventure, Story game where you play as Ajay who is on his way to escape the apocalyptic city along with his younger brother Aayu. On their way out to city they face many zombies, challenges and twists. But the question is can they escape this city full of monsters and problem?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/786abc7c78c018b7d21396e24957379e.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/5acf31e7a5d537fb005d2d059f21238c.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight different types of Zombies with different powers and defeat powerfull Monsters with different abilities and weakness. You will face high tech drones too, beware of them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/823eebe69aa586c4ee9031f21b6eef06.poster.avif?t=1772189407\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/823eebe69aa586c4ee9031f21b6eef06.webm?t=1772189407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/402124db020ca44872f593a393a671d1.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/5c6858f7d530ca3b11484e6053fa0ce3.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the puzzles, Fix broken things, Blow away walls, crack passcodes and more to unlock the story and progress forward</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/8de46f5c063f7ed6dd52e6e93cda9309.poster.avif?t=1772189407\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/8de46f5c063f7ed6dd52e6e93cda9309.webm?t=1772189407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/402124db020ca44872f593a393a671d1.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/e847556324e50ca7e5909e8b744ca0ac.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you uncover the story you will be haunted by a creepy creature in the darkness, extremely powerfull! It haunts you when you can't feel it's presence. Run or Die!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/d1d18f843211b9bda9a0e9edebed22bf.poster.avif?t=1772189407\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/d1d18f843211b9bda9a0e9edebed22bf.webm?t=1772189407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/786abc7c78c018b7d21396e24957379e.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Story Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Shooter Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Mini Games in Story Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Survive the Hunt</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Shoot, Collect, Craft, Shoot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Overcome Obstacles and Solve puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Different types of zombies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Boss Fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Different Guns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Semi Realistic Graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Atmospheric </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Mostly Dark and Horror Environment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Voiced Characters </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Fallow City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/fdbfde4fd9a01bd1c5a448e964520007.avif?t=1772189407\" width=600 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Fallow City is an Indie Horror, Action-Adventure, Story game where you play as Ajay who is on his way to escape the apocalyptic city along with his younger brother Aayu. On their way out to city they face many zombies, challenges and twists. But the question is can they escape this city full of monsters and problem?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/786abc7c78c018b7d21396e24957379e.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/5acf31e7a5d537fb005d2d059f21238c.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight different types of Zombies with different powers and defeat powerfull Monsters with different abilities and weakness. You will face high tech drones too, beware of them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/823eebe69aa586c4ee9031f21b6eef06.poster.avif?t=1772189407\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/823eebe69aa586c4ee9031f21b6eef06.webm?t=1772189407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph