teamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/d1d18f843211b9bda9a0e9edebed22bf.poster.avif?t=1772189407\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/d1d18f843211b9bda9a0e9edebed22bf.webm?t=1772189407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410980/extras/786abc7c78c018b7d21396e24957379e.webp?t=1772189407\" width=610 height=32 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Story Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Shooter Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Mini Games in Story Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Survive the Hunt</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Shoot, Collect, Craft, Shoot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Overcome Obstacles and Solve puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Different types of zombies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Boss Fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Different Guns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Semi Realistic Graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Atmospheric </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Mostly Dark and Horror Environment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > • Voiced Characters </p>",
